text.tspan: A: Submit signup form with valid Stripe token
C: Respond with subscription details (including wormhole code)
D: Respond with signup success page (including wormhole code)
F: Respond with pending subscriptions (including wormhole codes)
G: Establish wormhole for new pending subscription
H: Copy wormhole code (from D) to invite dialog
I: Attempt wormhole connect (with wormhole code from success page - D)
J{1,2}: Convey subscription details via wormhole
K: Mark subscription as active (was pending)
M:Respond with active subscriptions (including new active subscription)
N: Create subscription ConfigMap, Deployment, etc
